  "texts": [
    "For the cases in which the player profiles were missing, we set their heights and weights to 180 cm and 75 kg, respectively, as defaults.",
    "In total, we had 385 such occurrences out of a total of 213,246(= 22 × 9693) during data preprocessing.",
    "We downscaled the heights and weights by a factor of 100.",
    "Moreover, for each corner kick, we zero-centred the positions of on-pitch players and normalised them onto a 10 m × 10 m pitch, and their velocities were rescaled accordingly.",
    "For the cases in which the pitch dimensions were missing, we used a standard pitch dimension of 110 m × 63 m as default."
  ],
